{"tid":2449124,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"信用卡討論區（103）打定唔打？死唔去先好打！","createTime":"2021-03-16T12:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T12:06:16.000Z","uid":29744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6514973d7948cbd089faf5429bdda4d69523808a","tid":2449124,"uid":29744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">目錄</p></span></ins></strong><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>#1 FAQ<br />\n#2 集中討論卡種<br />\n#3 大學生懶人包</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">信用卡六誡</p></span></ins></strong><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">人妖，黑警，5毛，藍屍，左膠不可內進<br />\n不可張貼 MGM / referral link<br />\n不可張貼 Telegram 等 chat room link<br />\n發問前，先爬文<br />\n不可大肆宣傳中資卡<br />\n借定唔借，還得到先好借！</span></span></p><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">#1 FAQ</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ：年薪 $1,000,000 申請咩卡好？<br />\nA：八達通卡／易賞錢卡<br />\n<br />\nQ：想求 Member-Get-Member (MGM) 被推薦連結應該點做？<br />\nA：留低自己嘅聯絡分式 (e.g. Telegram) <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>重申本POST嚴禁貼 MGM LINK</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ：點申請年費豁免？<br />\nA：(1) 先致電年費豁免或客戶服務熱線 (2) 如未能豁免可考慮取消信用卡<br />\n<em>(收年費後一個月內取消，卡行一定會回水)</em><br />\n<br />\nQ：邊張信用卡好用／回贈高？<br />\nA：消費習慣因人而異，請自行比較：<br />\n  &mdash; 想要現金回贈／里數／積分換禮品？<br />\n  &mdash; 迎新禮品啱唔啱駛？<br />\n  &mdash; 每月消費幾多？<br />\n  &mdash; 主要消費模式？<br />\n  &mdash; 手上有咩卡？<br />\n<br />\nQ：邊張卡 O! ePay／PayMe／WeChat Pay／支付寶HK 有分？<br />\nA：Google<br />\n<br />\nQ：八達通自動增值 (AAVS)、網上繳費用邊張好？<br />\nA：睇<span class=\"red\">#2</span><ins>集中討論卡種</ins><br />\n<br />\nQ：迎新／推廣嘅里數／積分／回贈幾時先有？<br />\nA：睇 T&amp;C<br />\n<br />\nQ：點解有啲卡你地唔講嘅？<br />\nA：狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">實用 Link</p></span></ins></strong><br />\n信用卡討論區（103）安心出賣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2413709/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla